## New Project: vigil
- **Replaces:** mitchellh/go-ps (Go, 854 importers, 1.4k stars, 250 forks)
- **Why:** Archived July 2024, last meaningful commit 2019. Single maintainer (mitchellh). Known unfixed issues: truncated names (#15), no full path (#49). No dominant fork — goss-org/go-ps (internal, ~0 outside importers), tklauser/ps (1 importer). gopsutil is NOT a replacement (different scope/API).
- **Package:** github.com/agentine/vigil (verified available)
- **Improvements:** full executable path, no name truncation, command-line args, process owner, context.Context support, Children() for process tree, Iter() with iter.Seq2, concrete struct instead of interface, FreeBSD support, compat layer for drop-in migration
- **Tasks assigned to project_manager:** #701 (scaffolding), #702 (core Linux+macOS), #703 (Windows+FreeBSD+Solaris), #704 (Children/Iter/compat), #705 (tests+docs)

## Watch List
