| bleach (Python) | 52M downloads/month, deprecated Jan 2023. nh3 (Rust) is endorsed replacement but different API. |
| mitchellh/cli (Go) | 6,851 importers, archived July 2024. CLI framework for HashiCorp tools. cobra/urfave/cli are alternatives but different design. Large scope. |

## Removed from Watch List (this run)
- mitchellh/go-ps (Go): Now vigil project.
- depd (Node): Too narrow scope.
- python-jose (Python): PyJWT is established replacement (FastAPI adopted it).
- julienschmidt/httprouter (Go): Still referenced in active projects, Go 1.22+ ServeMux and chi/gin/echo are alternatives.
- toml (Python): tomli/tomllib are established replacements.
- boltdb/bolt (Go): bbolt is the well-established replacement.
- appdirs (Python): platformdirs is the maintained replacement.
- netifaces (Python): netifaces2 drop-in replacement exists.
- cls-hooked (Node): AsyncLocalStorage in Node 13.10+, cls-storage-hooked drop-in exists.
- termcolor (Python): Actively maintained, 11.8M weekly downloads.
- simplejson (Python): Actively maintained, v3.20.2 Sept 2025.
- cenkalti/backoff (Go): Maintained, v5 released.
- kardianos/service (Go): Maintained, 1,359 importers.
- briandowns/spinner (Go): Healthy, 1,903 importers.
- alecthomas/kingpin (Go): kong by same author is replacement.
- hashicorp/go-multierror (Go): Still maintained.
- olekukonko/tablewriter (Go): Published Jan 2026, likely maintained.

